{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述了陆小凤前往宫九舱房进行谈判的过程。沙曼在出发前与小玉深谈，感谢她的帮助并邀请她加入。陆小凤发现宫九有自虐的变态嗜好，但宫九随后恢复正常，两人展开紧张的谈判。陆小凤用牛肉汤的命换取四人一个时辰的逃生时间，宫九同意但警告这是最后一次。谈判结束后，陆小凤、老实和尚和小玉乘小艇离开，牛肉汤试图捣乱拖延时间，被陆小凤扔进海里。本章揭示了宫九的真面目，展现了陆小凤的智慧和勇气。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是从小跟着他们兄妹的？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从我七岁的时候，我是个孤儿，若不是老爷子救了我，我早就淹死在海里。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你对宫家的人，一直都很忠心？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "曼姑娘如果想跟我聊天，到了小艇上我们一定有很多时间可以聊。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九少爷是个怎么样的人，你当然很清楚？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在陆小凤去找他了，这一去很可能不会回来。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一死，宫主也得死，我们就没有一个人能活，所以……",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我有句话一定要先跟你说。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这句话曼姑娘是不是一定要现在说？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这句话只有三个字。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三个字？哪三个字？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我们是在冒险，可是如果没有你，我们就连这种机会都得不到，所以，如果我们这次都能活下去，我希望你能永远跟我们在一起。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是个很会吃醋的女人，可是这次我说的是真心话。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我今年已经十六岁了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆小凤是个很讨人喜欢的男人，我相信一定有很多女孩子都喜欢他。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然不能说我不喜欢他，可是……",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我这样做并不是为了他。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绝不是。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你是为了我？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也不是。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是为了我自己。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你并不需要来冒这种险的？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有原因。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能不能告诉我？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在还不能。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要陆小凤能活着回来，我一定会告诉你的，就算你们不想听都不行。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快来救我，我已忍不住啦！",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鞭子……鞭子……",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "用鞭子抽我……用力抽我……",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你，快……快拿鞭子！",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是在等宫主？她喜欢用鞭子抽人，我不喜欢。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你喜欢什么？喜欢沙曼？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若以为那女人是个淑女，你就错了，她是婊子。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她是个不折不扣的婊子，为了块肥肉就肯陪人上床睡觉，她十三岁的时候就已经陪人上床睡觉。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是生气了？因为你也知道我说的是真话？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是宫九。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道！",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是宫九？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你一定想不到我会来找你？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上不怕死的人很多，并不止你一个。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怕死。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你现在一定很后悔。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后悔？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后悔刚才为什么不杀了我。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才我的确有机会杀了你的。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没有。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有杀你，是我的错，我并不想要你感激，可是你……",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你是不是已明白了？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明白什么？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你刚才并没有错，因为你根本没有机会。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以，你也不必对我感激。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你现在非死不可了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论谁做出了不该做的事，都非死不可。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况我还看见了一些不该看的事。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜现在我还不能杀你。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你从不免费杀人？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为了你，这一点我也可破例。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为的什么？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她在哪里？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在箱子里面。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道我问的是谁？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也知道她已落入我们手里？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怕死，可是你来了，你当然不是来送死的。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你准备用她的命，来换你们两条命？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是两条命，是四条命。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有两条命是老实和尚和小玉的？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要的是——",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只要一个时辰。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我带她走，你的船回转，一个时辰后我放她走。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船上的两条小艇你都已夺下？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道小玉一定不会让我失望。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个时辰，你就让她来跟我会合？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四个人用不着两条小艇，其中一条就是为她准备的。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想得很周到。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说话也算数。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有不多说话的人，说话才算数。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看我像是个多嘴的人，",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能忘记这几天看见的事？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能替我们保守秘密？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们的事我就算说出来，又有谁会相信？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你好像从不轻易答应别人一件事？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的！",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不轻易许诺的人，就不会寡信。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我总是尽力去做。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我相信她回来的时候一定平安无恙。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也相信现在小艇一定已放了下去。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么只要等你一下去，就可以看见这条船已回头了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟你谈交易，的确是件很愉快的事。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也一样。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只希望这是最后一次了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最后一次相见？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下次你再见到我时，我相信彼此都不会有这么愉快了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也相信。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的见到了宫九？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他究竟是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们已见过面，但你却还是不知道？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只知道一点。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我绝不想再看见他，也绝不想跟他交手了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜有些事就算你真的不想去做，有时却又偏偏非去做不可。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道我一定还会看见他？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "宫九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在时候一定已经到了，我们已经应该放她走。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还不走？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为什么要走？这箱子里又暖又舒服。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不想去见你的九哥？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若不回去，他迟早总会追上来的，我一点都不急。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和尚有多久没有看过脱光的女人了？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像……好像已经有几百年了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "佛家讲究眼中有色，心中无色，和尚为什么不敢看我？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和尚的道行还不够。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道和尚心里有鬼么？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有一点。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "坐在和尚怀里去，原来比躺在箱子里还舒服得多。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和尚有多久没摸过女人了？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不……不知道。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是不知道，还是忘记了？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是……是忘记了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "和尚一定连摸女人是什么滋味都忘了，让我来提醒你。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "割掉系船的绳子，她上去也好，不上去也好，都不关我们的事了。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果她一定要淹死，我们怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们也只有看着。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好办法，好主意。",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆小凤，你这个王八蛋！我绝不会饶了你的，总有一天我要把你切碎了煮来吃！",
      "tone": "neutral",
      "chapter": 14
    }
